  <brief_title>Dose Escalation With SIB to Intraprostatic/Lymphatic GTV in High Risk Prostate Cancer</brief_title>
  <acronym>PARAPLY-1</acronym>
  <official_title>Phase 2 Study of High Risk Prostatae Cancer Treated With Dose-escalated Simultaneous Integrated Boost to Prostate and Lymph Node GTV</official_title>
